{"tid":1026413,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"落雨竟然有靚女遮我依個小毒撚...","createTime":"2019-02-18T06:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T11:17:20.000Z","uid":71508,"like":7,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5bfc4bea8e593b9bf3cdbcbe98008ff729c77808","tid":1026413,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:00:50.000Z","msg":"是咁的...頭先放學係MK搭巴士返屋企,點知落雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,但係條人龍已經好長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果一行開就要等多幾部車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,咁好唯有企定定比雨係咁淋落我個毒撚頭到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個時候我旁邊個位靚女姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拎左把縮骨遮出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我心諗:唉個撚個都有遮<br />\n幾時先有車黎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個頭都塔哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,呢個時候姐姐就講:不如我遮埋你啦 <br />\n我心諗:唉連佢旁邊個呀叔都有人遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毒撚係無人鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知我偷偷地由佢隻腳咁望上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (平時我唔敢望人)點知佢竟然係同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我就話:唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,之後佢叫我行埋D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為把遮太細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係個一刻我希望部巴士永遠唔去黎,而我望去佢旁邊既呀叔竟然用葡萄既眼神望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我呢世人係第1次比人葡萄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來個種感覺係咁好架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後巴士黎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 姐姐就同我講:你上先啦,我要等朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然個一刻好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係佢竟然同我個BYEBYE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上到上層既時候我就用唔捨得既眼神向姐姐說再見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e97794a176106446f1048b4e05aec470fe53790","tid":1026413,"uid":838,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:04:04.000Z","msg":"中學生涯未試過被靚女遮是否人生遺憾？"},{"pid":"b6b6bb0cfe33cca64e9035145606bbdfd322e70e","tid":1026413,"uid":151411,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:05:53.000Z","msg":"好心你咁大個人就唔好ff咁多啦"},{"pid":"59640a04feed561dc7056fccabf998b3c9a1b5ac","tid":1026413,"uid":217450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:08:19.000Z","msg":"&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"9bbea2b6f7458d9e2cab25b0d729cabd0ae59a5d","tid":1026413,"uid":19978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:15:13.000Z","msg":"咁好想象力，寫小說啦"},{"pid":"e39e8b75df91d469e9bf5c8eeecd3041a95a5497","tid":1026413,"uid":187893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:16:12.000Z","msg":"好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbcb7b7f777030dac3c6354938258dbb99de68d2","tid":1026413,"uid":49574,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:20:44.000Z","msg":"個天落雨就係想淋撚醒你"},{"pid":"c593792a5777c35fc9095ed7ba45331da404b548","tid":1026413,"uid":71508,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:21:53.000Z","msg":"［香港人］都係想遮埋你唔想你淋雨啫<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1026137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1026137</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n多謝依位巴打<br />\n令我有得俾靚女遮"},{"pid":"12f0d883ae64e66fe9092080ca2712f39edb2660","tid":1026413,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:22:42.000Z","msg":"咁大個人就唔好ff啦。jpg"},{"pid":"7be873375ae629830cdc534ea